01:02:20,132 --> 01:02:21,602
Okay.

807
01:02:23,032 --> 01:02:26,102
Jae Sook took escorted the
old lady to her house.

808
01:02:26,742 --> 01:02:27,872
I see.

809
01:02:32,442 --> 01:02:33,882
- Well...
- Yes?

810
01:02:34,982 --> 01:02:36,112
What?

811
01:02:39,352 --> 01:02:40,522
Nothing.

812
01:02:52,362 --> 01:02:54,202
I hope he keeps him safe...

813
01:02:54,832 --> 01:02:56,472
and sends him back.

814
01:02:58,572 --> 01:03:00,142
I hope he does.

815
01:03:19,362 --> 01:03:23,162
Get out of my sight, please.

816
01:04:31,662 --> 01:04:33,038
You really don't know?

817
01:04:33,062 --> 01:04:36,132
I don't. He doesn't have a mobile phone.

818
01:04:36,332 --> 01:04:38,342
Can I go home after organizing this?

819
01:04:40,242 --> 01:04:42,642
The director didn't say anything...

820
01:04:42,812 --> 01:04:44,582
and we didn't hear from him for a few days.

821
01:04:45,042 --> 01:04:46,942
Maybe he didn't like this place.

822
01:04:47,042 --> 01:04:49,552
He should have said goodbye
if he was leaving.

823
01:04:49,812 --> 01:04:52,352
- I'm sad.
- You're right.

824
01:04:52,822 --> 01:04:54,691
You feel empty...

825
01:04:54,692 --> 01:04:55,992
when someone leaves.

826
01:04:56,822 --> 01:04:58,022
Were you sad?

827
01:04:59,862 --> 01:05:00,862
Really?

828
01:05:00,863 --> 01:05:03,591
You'll feel sad when I leave.

829
01:05:03,592 --> 01:05:07,002
- Okay.
- How could you feel sad for him?

830
01:05:07,772 --> 01:05:10,172
You only knew him for a few days.
Wait and see when I leave.

831
01:05:11,902 --> 01:05:12,902
Is he here?

832
01:05:27,892 --> 01:05:31,361
(Shinhae Oriental Medicine Hospital)

833
01:05:31,362 --> 01:05:33,792
(The opening ceremony of the VIP ward)

834
01:05:34,292 --> 01:05:35,292
Thank you.

835
01:05:36,532 --> 01:05:39,001
We ambitiously prepared...

836
01:05:39,002 --> 01:05:42,332
the VIP ward of Shinhae
Oriental Medicine Hospital.

837
01:05:42,472 --> 01:05:45,178
Based on our long history
of medical technology...

838
01:05:45,202 --> 01:05:48,518
and excellent personnel,

839
01:05:48,542 --> 01:05:52,582
this ward will become the stepping stone...

840
01:05:52,682 --> 01:05:56,458
of upgrading the level
of oriental medicine,

841
01:05:56,482 --> 01:05:58,362
and become a worldwide
oriental medical center.

842
01:06:11,932 --> 01:06:13,862
Next, Dr. Yoo.

843
01:06:19,572 --> 01:06:22,342
Hello, I'm Yoo Jae Ha.

844
01:06:30,652 --> 01:06:33,851
The players are exceptional here.

845
01:06:33,852 --> 01:06:34,852
Yes.

846
01:06:36,052 --> 01:06:38,761
We still have one more person left.

847
01:06:38,762 --> 01:06:40,632
Really?

848
01:06:41,592 --> 01:06:42,762
He's coming.

849
01:07:14,962 --> 01:07:17,761
I am sorry, I am a little late.

850
01:07:17,762 --> 01:07:19,031
You're just in time.

851
01:07:19,032 --> 01:07:20,432
Okay, introduce yourself.

852
01:07:28,642 --> 01:07:29,812
Nice to meet you.

853
01:07:31,512 --> 01:07:33,442
I am oriental medicine doctor, Heo...

854
01:07:37,112 --> 01:07:38,322
Bong Tak.

855
01:08:14,152 --> 01:08:17,092
(Live Up To Your Name, Dr.
Heo/Deserving of the Name)

856
01:08:17,592 --> 01:08:20,062
Heo Im, you became a different person.

857
01:08:21,062 --> 01:08:22,331
Heo Im came.

858
01:08:22,332 --> 01:08:24,031
What will you do this time?

859
01:08:24,032 --> 01:08:25,501
What does he have to do with you?

860
01:08:25,502 --> 01:08:27,932
I'm getting to know him.

861
01:08:28,632 --> 01:08:31,041
I'm playing games? With whom?

862
01:08:31,042 --> 01:08:34,041
I will walk the path that I could
not walk when I was there.

863
01:08:34,042 --> 01:08:35,612
This must be stress.

864
01:08:36,342 --> 01:08:38,181
Will a strong background win? Or skill?

865
01:08:38,182 --> 01:08:41,111
Why did you let him in
here in the beginning?

866
01:08:41,112 --> 01:08:43,628
I will become a doctor who becomes
happy when he saves lives,

867
01:08:43,652 --> 01:08:45,652
and glad when he heals people.

